definitions.definition: To brood , raise , or maintain eggs, organisms, or living tissue through the provision of ideal environmental conditions.
To incubate metaphorically; to ponder an idea slowly and deliberately as if in preparation for hatching it.

main_definition: ( transitive ) To brood , raise , or maintain eggs, organisms, or living tissue through the provision of ideal environmental conditions.
secondary_definitions: ( transitive , figurative ) To incubate metaphorically; to ponder an idea slowly and deliberately as if in preparation for hatching it.
